beer.beer_description:
Our Signature Dark Ale from the Cascadian IPA family is something we’re really proud of. It’s malt and hop profile give the illusion of a heavy stout but the taste of a light IPA.
The rich colour comes from the midnight wheat, resulting in a beer with a deep rich colour without the astringent and bitter taste that black malts can attribute.
Its great beer all year round and will leave you wanting to put back another one.
